|date=[[25 July]] [[2000]]
|accessdate=2008-02-07
|publisher=BBC Sport}}</ref> City subsequently lost both legs. Wetherall started the league season but after playing all 52 league games since joining Bradford without leaving the field, Wetherall limped off before half-time during a 2&ndash;0 defeat to their nearest rivals [[Derby County F.C.|Derby County]] in November 2000.<ref>{{cite news
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/1028654.stm
